5
00:00:45,885 --> 00:00:51,255
It's special because Sang-min gave it to me

6
00:00:51,957 --> 00:00:55,895
He must know that I like him

7
00:00:55,895 --> 00:01:00,889
Thought he wouldn't
when you stare at him everyday?

8
00:01:01,400 --> 00:01:04,270
Go give this to Sang-min

9
00:01:04,270 --> 00:01:08,007
No, you give it to him
I'm not going there

10
00:01:08,007 --> 00:01:09,565
Why not?

11
00:01:10,209 --> 00:01:12,541
Did you and Soo-gyung fight?

12
00:01:14,780 --> 00:01:19,012
Remember when it suddenly rained that day?

13
00:01:19,351 --> 00:01:23,219
Sang-min was drinking coffee here

14
00:01:23,989 --> 00:01:28,050
He was looking out of the window

15
00:01:28,127 --> 00:01:32,860
then suddenly turned to me and said

16
00:01:34,734 --> 00:01:39,000
"Did you bring an umbrella?"

17
00:01:39,338 --> 00:01:44,241
And then I said
"I was worried I didn't"

18
00:01:45,044 --> 00:01:50,346
He placed his umbrella here

19
00:01:50,950 --> 00:01:54,579
and said
"You can have it"

20
00:01:55,121 --> 00:01:57,851
He said he was okay to get wet

21
00:01:58,057 --> 00:02:01,925
And then he ran off in the rain

22
00:02:10,870 --> 00:02:13,862
Did you bring an umbrella?

23
00:02:18,577 --> 00:02:21,512
You can have it.

24
00:02:26,852 --> 00:02:31,290
It's raining a lot outside

25
00:02:31,290 --> 00:02:35,989
