26
00:02:52,545 --> 00:02:57,380
This is a really special umbrella

27
00:02:58,651 --> 00:03:02,553
I'll give it back to him

28
00:03:09,395 --> 00:03:12,455
Did you bring an umbrella?

29
00:03:12,631 --> 00:03:14,266
Of course, I did

30
00:03:14,266 --> 00:03:15,699
Really?

31
00:03:17,336 --> 00:03:18,997
But still, take mine

32
00:03:24,376 --> 00:03:25,900
Is she crazy?

33
00:04:45,057 --> 00:04:48,584
You have an umbrella
but why are you so soaked?

34
00:04:49,862 --> 00:04:53,389
It's not mine

35
00:04:53,632 --> 00:04:56,066
I came to return it to you

36
00:04:56,735 --> 00:04:59,431
You left it at the store

37
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:08,637
I'm not the only one
who gets wet even with an umbrella, am I?

38
00:05:14,620 --> 00:05:16,451
Don't go

39
00:05:27,866 --> 00:05:30,164
You already know...

40
00:05:30,669 --> 00:05:32,796
my feelings

41
00:05:36,408 --> 00:05:38,706
Now, you know it all

42
00:05:44,550 --> 00:05:46,177
Yeah

43
00:05:48,187 --> 00:05:51,384
